column5: nuffing better to do….  house has never been so freekin clean.

a one armed housecleaner.... what a concept.   Art it took me 4 days do get it clean with one arm…not bad considering we aint the neat and tidy types
when you are done with that you can take up one armed juggling.   Art
when you are done with that you can take up one armed juggling.   Art  i can only think of smutty replies to that….lol.

I said Juggling not Giggling lol   Art
